WEBVTT

00:00:11.440 --> 00:00:12.210
Minwoo.

00:00:15.250 --> 00:00:17.510
Let's not continue with the treatments.

00:00:20.750 --> 00:00:21.470
Why?

00:00:23.490 --> 00:00:25.150
You no longer need treatment?

00:00:27.890 --> 00:00:28.860
I...

00:00:35.180 --> 00:00:37.180
Your treatment has been going well,

00:00:38.390 --> 00:00:40.400
and your mental state has improved a lot.

00:00:40.400 --> 00:00:41.240
Am I wrong?

00:00:44.300 --> 00:00:45.250
You're right.

00:00:46.960 --> 00:00:47.800
My body

00:00:48.090 --> 00:00:49.020
and mental state

00:00:49.670 --> 00:00:50.590
have improved.

00:00:51.790 --> 00:00:52.390
Thank you.

00:00:54.630 --> 00:00:55.530
But you know,

00:00:57.300 --> 00:00:59.160
dwelling too much on past traumas

00:01:00.490 --> 00:01:02.090
can make you trapped in them.

00:01:04.120 --> 00:01:06.120
You'll only sink deeper and deeper.

00:01:10.260 --> 00:01:11.720
What I should really learn

00:01:13.270 --> 00:01:15.050
is not to erase the past,

00:01:16.610 --> 00:01:18.170
but to learn to accept it.

00:01:21.070 --> 00:01:22.760
Looking at myself from

00:01:24.150 --> 00:01:25.750
someone else's perspective

00:01:26.800 --> 00:01:28.400
is the most important thing.

00:01:33.870 --> 00:01:34.920
Someone else?

00:01:35.979 --> 00:01:37.280
Do you mean Kim Haejun?

00:01:39.900 --> 00:01:41.830
Ever since you started seeing him,

00:01:41.830 --> 00:01:42.759
you know best...

00:01:45.130 --> 00:01:46.750
how your life

00:01:48.530 --> 00:01:50.030
has changed.

00:01:52.160 --> 00:01:53.070
Am I wrong?

00:01:57.070 --> 00:01:58.250
What do you mean?

00:02:00.630 --> 00:02:01.760
In the past, at least

00:02:02.720 --> 00:02:04.120
you knew what you wanted.

00:02:04.910 --> 00:02:06.220
But now...

00:02:09.930 --> 00:02:11.130
you're too unstable.

00:02:12.950 --> 00:02:15.400
Kim Haejun can't give you anything.

00:02:19.790 --> 00:02:20.870
But because of him,

00:02:21.200 --> 00:02:23.240
you're trying to change yourself.

00:02:25.500 --> 00:02:26.829
Why won't you choose me?

00:02:29.020 --> 00:02:31.420
We know each other
better than anyone else.

00:02:33.280 --> 00:02:34.630
Over 20 years,

00:02:35.400 --> 00:02:37.130
you've been the only one for me.

00:02:39.640 --> 00:02:41.100
So why won't you choose me?

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:43.820
I...

00:02:45.220 --> 00:02:46.250
At the very least,

00:02:47.850 --> 00:02:48.520
I thought

00:02:48.770 --> 00:02:50.370
I was someone special to you.

00:02:59.310 --> 00:03:01.310
I chose to be with Haejun

00:03:04.100 --> 00:03:05.770
because he is him.

00:03:07.830 --> 00:03:09.230
There's no other reason.

00:03:11.780 --> 00:03:13.980
Yes, he and I lived in different worlds.

00:03:15.050 --> 00:03:16.270
But the light on him

00:03:18.510 --> 00:03:20.640
illuminates the darkness in my heart.

00:03:23.220 --> 00:03:24.820
Of course, you're right that

00:03:25.720 --> 00:03:29.450
there are still pockets of darkness
that he hasn't reached. But...

00:03:29.640 --> 00:03:31.500
I still want to take a gamble

00:03:32.920 --> 00:03:34.850
that he'll completely light me up.

00:03:37.650 --> 00:03:38.400
Minwoo.

00:03:39.930 --> 00:03:41.020
I don't want to deny

00:03:42.640 --> 00:03:44.170
our 20 years of friendship.

00:03:45.030 --> 00:03:46.300
Thank you for

00:03:47.340 --> 00:03:48.340
those good times.

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:51.800
But some things can't be forced.

00:03:55.050 --> 00:03:56.310
Don't come here again.

00:04:10.110 --> 00:04:11.150
Minwoo!

00:04:12.750 --> 00:04:14.280
Why's he leaving in a hurry?

00:04:15.450 --> 00:04:16.980
Someone must have hurt him.

00:04:19.399 --> 00:04:20.390
Focus.

00:04:23.210 --> 00:04:25.210
You need more of this here.

00:05:00.850 --> 00:05:01.900
I'll get going.

00:05:01.920 --> 00:05:03.020
Take care.

00:05:06.560 --> 00:05:08.440
He said I improved a lot!

00:05:14.180 --> 00:05:15.310
Soohyung praised me

00:05:15.900 --> 00:05:18.070
for making great progress today.

00:05:20.630 --> 00:05:21.200
Really?

00:05:23.250 --> 00:05:24.440
So you

00:05:25.050 --> 00:05:26.670
are fond of him?

00:05:27.250 --> 00:05:27.630
Yeah.

00:05:28.620 --> 00:05:30.970
He's more impressive than I thought.

00:05:31.540 --> 00:05:33.050
He seems frivolous, but he actually

00:05:33.050 --> 00:05:35.110
graduated from an art school abroad.

00:05:53.460 --> 00:05:54.500
It seems that

00:05:57.300 --> 00:05:58.900
I've been too nice to you.

00:06:01.360 --> 00:06:03.090
How dare you praise another man

00:06:04.500 --> 00:06:06.070
in front of me?

00:06:07.820 --> 00:06:09.270
That's not what I meant.

00:06:10.230 --> 00:06:11.490
Then what did you mean?

00:06:14.850 --> 00:06:15.950
You know, I saw that

00:06:17.820 --> 00:06:19.810
you two were very close.

00:06:27.100 --> 00:06:28.360
He touched your hands,

00:06:30.300 --> 00:06:31.560
stared at your wrists,

00:06:35.659 --> 00:06:36.520
and your ear...

00:06:46.050 --> 00:06:47.780
His ear was so close to your ear.

00:06:49.570 --> 00:06:52.030
Do you have to be so intimate
for an art class?

00:06:52.810 --> 00:06:53.550
What?

00:06:54.810 --> 00:06:56.650
Do you want to sleep with him?

00:06:58.090 --> 00:06:59.550
Have you thought about it?

00:07:01.020 --> 00:07:02.100
Yes or no?

00:07:52.470 --> 00:07:53.370
How dare you

00:07:54.780 --> 00:07:55.680
bite me?

00:08:00.300 --> 00:08:02.270
Can you please let me explain?

00:08:04.580 --> 00:08:06.980
There's really nothing between him and me.

00:08:08.230 --> 00:08:10.230
Why won't you hear me out? Why?

00:08:14.880 --> 00:08:16.270
In my opinion,

00:08:17.950 --> 00:08:19.920
you don't need extra lessons.

00:08:21.390 --> 00:08:23.050
So what if you can't graduate?

00:08:23.810 --> 00:08:25.740
What use would all that drawing be?

00:08:25.850 --> 00:08:28.050
Can you make money even if you graduate?

00:08:32.130 --> 00:08:35.169
I can arrange a good job for you.

00:08:36.710 --> 00:08:39.730
Why can't you see how lucky you are?

00:08:41.900 --> 00:08:42.850
Look!

00:08:44.049 --> 00:08:45.550
Look carefully.

00:08:46.940 --> 00:08:48.250
This villa.

00:08:48.940 --> 00:08:49.670
This house.

00:08:49.950 --> 00:08:50.800
My house!

00:08:51.370 --> 00:08:52.230
How great is it?

00:08:53.170 --> 00:08:54.450
Can you ever afford it?

00:08:54.540 --> 00:08:55.370
You can't.

00:08:57.040 --> 00:08:59.000
Why don't you know how lucky you are

00:08:59.000 --> 00:09:00.960
and insist on going out to work?

00:09:01.120 --> 00:09:02.620
Leave then.

00:09:06.870 --> 00:09:08.870
I never thought of depending on you.

00:09:10.050 --> 00:09:12.200
You overestimate yourself!

00:09:12.740 --> 00:09:13.430
Fine.

00:09:28.700 --> 00:09:29.550
You actually

00:09:30.520 --> 00:09:31.600
really left?

00:09:43.690 --> 00:09:46.020
How could he say
such hurtful things to me?

00:09:46.530 --> 00:09:48.520
He thinks he's so great.

00:09:51.290 --> 00:09:52.620
There's not even a taxi.

00:09:55.320 --> 00:09:56.640
Do I have to walk home?

00:10:11.190 --> 00:10:12.570
Did Jaehun kick you out?

00:10:13.570 --> 00:10:14.500
Why are you here?

00:10:14.970 --> 00:10:16.300
I told you

00:10:16.670 --> 00:10:18.170
you were not compatible.

00:10:19.640 --> 00:10:21.620
Who are you to say that?

00:10:22.890 --> 00:10:24.570
We can solve our problems

00:10:25.300 --> 00:10:26.150
by ourselves.

00:10:27.770 --> 00:10:29.770
You have no right to interfere.

00:10:30.380 --> 00:10:31.510
Your relationship?

00:10:32.470 --> 00:10:34.400
How long have you known each other?

00:10:35.450 --> 00:10:36.550
He just...

00:10:37.250 --> 00:10:38.240
He just

00:10:38.550 --> 00:10:40.720
got with you on impulse.

00:10:43.250 --> 00:10:44.170
Don't tell me

00:10:44.600 --> 00:10:46.400
you think you're special to him?

00:10:47.030 --> 00:10:48.430
Don't flatter yourself.

00:10:50.090 --> 00:10:51.550
I think the value of love is

00:10:53.170 --> 00:10:57.030
based on the depth of your love
and not how long you've spent together.

00:10:59.800 --> 00:11:01.220
Someone like you

00:11:02.650 --> 00:11:04.320
can never win his heart

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:06.300
even if you spend 30 years by his side.

00:11:06.300 --> 00:11:08.030
Who are you to say that about me?

00:11:28.760 --> 00:11:30.620
Didn't I make myself clear today?

00:11:32.600 --> 00:11:35.060
I was naive to think
that you had principles.

00:11:36.170 --> 00:11:37.620
I overestimated

00:11:38.670 --> 00:11:40.420
our 20 years of friendship.

00:11:47.230 --> 00:11:48.400
For old times' sake,

00:11:48.400 --> 00:11:50.400
I don't want to be harsh.

00:11:51.290 --> 00:11:53.270
So get out of my sight right now.

00:12:53.150 --> 00:12:54.210
I'll do it myself.

00:13:00.040 --> 00:13:01.040
Don't move.

00:13:02.500 --> 00:13:03.960
You've been out for so long.

00:13:03.960 --> 00:13:06.490
You're lucky that
you didn't freeze to death.

00:13:09.980 --> 00:13:11.240
Are you still mad at me?

00:13:13.580 --> 00:13:15.110
I should be asking you that.

00:13:15.440 --> 00:13:17.300
Who got angry and ran out just now?

00:13:21.530 --> 00:13:23.330
I didn't expect to walk that far.

00:13:26.140 --> 00:13:27.650
I was angry and ran out,

00:13:29.690 --> 00:13:31.550
but I went further than I thought.

00:13:42.720 --> 00:13:43.800
You know what?

00:13:45.140 --> 00:13:47.670
You're acting like a female lead
in a tragedy.

00:13:50.430 --> 00:13:51.000
Then,

00:13:52.720 --> 00:13:54.150
are you the male lead?

00:14:12.680 --> 00:14:14.010
Don't be angry anymore.

00:14:16.420 --> 00:14:17.130
Do you

00:14:18.520 --> 00:14:21.070
really not know why I'm angry?

00:14:25.870 --> 00:14:26.500
I do.

00:14:29.530 --> 00:14:31.730
Because I didn't respect your thoughts

00:14:32.910 --> 00:14:34.310
and said hurtful things.

00:14:37.610 --> 00:14:39.450
Your life is yours to decide.

00:14:41.450 --> 00:14:42.450
But I actually...

00:14:43.970 --> 00:14:46.300
Maybe it's because we've gotten close...

00:14:48.320 --> 00:14:50.320
I should've shown you more respect.

00:14:52.970 --> 00:14:53.620
I'm sorry.

00:14:55.870 --> 00:14:56.930
I don't understand

00:14:59.180 --> 00:15:01.440
why I'm so afraid that you will leave me.

00:15:04.660 --> 00:15:05.950
I trust you.

00:15:07.880 --> 00:15:08.670
So...

00:15:11.060 --> 00:15:12.390
you should trust me too.

00:15:29.990 --> 00:15:30.790
What's wrong?

00:15:31.170 --> 00:15:32.900
Is Jaehun still not picking up?

00:15:33.940 --> 00:15:34.460
Yeah.

00:15:35.810 --> 00:15:37.610
This has never happened before.

00:15:39.810 --> 00:15:41.530
Oh, come on,

00:15:42.140 --> 00:15:43.470
you know what he's like.

00:15:50.550 --> 00:15:52.550
Once he makes a decision,

00:15:53.310 --> 00:15:54.640
he will never turn back.

00:15:57.690 --> 00:15:59.920
Especially when it concerns
his special someone,

00:15:59.920 --> 00:16:01.480
his painkiller.

00:16:03.160 --> 00:16:04.310
That Kim Haejun

00:16:05.430 --> 00:16:07.860
is the one he really wants to protect.

00:16:08.980 --> 00:16:10.630
And you crossed the line.

00:16:12.630 --> 00:16:14.430
You tried to hurt the one

00:16:14.790 --> 00:16:15.920
he wants to protect.

00:16:17.850 --> 00:16:20.110
You failed, but you've antagonized him.

00:16:21.320 --> 00:16:22.150
Minwoo.

00:16:22.960 --> 00:16:24.160
You were too anxious.

00:16:28.390 --> 00:16:30.250
How could our 20-year friendship

00:16:31.240 --> 00:16:31.990
lose to

00:16:33.460 --> 00:16:35.050
a six-month relationship?

00:16:36.200 --> 00:16:37.600
That's the power of love.

00:16:39.140 --> 00:16:40.140
Isn't it amazing?

00:16:41.300 --> 00:16:42.960
Between sunlight and shadow,

00:16:43.650 --> 00:16:45.780
what will the one who yearns for warmth

00:16:46.180 --> 00:16:47.200
choose?

00:16:50.520 --> 00:16:51.570
Just give up.

00:16:52.780 --> 00:16:54.270
Even without Jaehun,

00:16:54.870 --> 00:16:56.130
I'm still by your side.

00:16:57.590 --> 00:16:59.200
I have no feelings for you.

00:17:48.520 --> 00:17:49.720
Why'd you laugh at me?

00:17:51.750 --> 00:17:52.900
I didn't.

00:17:54.170 --> 00:17:54.970
I just thought

00:17:55.300 --> 00:17:56.370
you're cute.

00:17:58.620 --> 00:17:59.590
Then...

00:18:01.060 --> 00:18:02.080
Join me.

00:18:03.290 --> 00:18:05.420
This dance is very popular these days.

00:18:06.900 --> 00:18:08.050
I don't want to.

00:18:08.610 --> 00:18:09.580
It looks stupid.

00:18:10.550 --> 00:18:12.010
You just mocked me, right?

00:18:13.750 --> 00:18:15.200
Do it with me.

00:18:15.590 --> 00:18:17.270
Or I'll really get mad.

00:18:17.270 --> 00:18:18.390
Do you hear me?

00:18:18.390 --> 00:18:19.330
Come on.

00:18:22.110 --> 00:18:22.740
Fine.

00:18:45.170 --> 00:18:46.940
You're so bad at dancing!

00:18:50.400 --> 00:18:51.000
Hey.

00:18:52.340 --> 00:18:53.140
You've been

00:18:55.670 --> 00:18:57.730
teasing me too much, don't you think?

00:18:57.960 --> 00:18:58.880
Huh?

00:19:10.580 --> 00:19:11.700
What are you doing?

00:19:21.340 --> 00:19:22.460
OK, OK.

00:19:23.020 --> 00:19:24.030
I was wrong.

00:19:24.350 --> 00:19:25.390
I'm sorry.

00:19:25.520 --> 00:19:26.460
OK, OK.

00:19:26.700 --> 00:19:27.740
I know I was wrong.

00:19:31.440 --> 00:19:32.370
Bingo!

00:19:33.200 --> 00:19:34.370
"Bingo," huh?

00:19:35.270 --> 00:19:36.410
You started it.

00:19:39.600 --> 00:19:41.080
You didn't get me!

00:19:48.340 --> 00:19:49.870
I don't wanna play anymore.

00:19:50.340 --> 00:19:51.210
I'm leaving.

00:19:52.660 --> 00:19:53.990
Where are you going now?

00:21:23.630 --> 00:21:24.350
Kim Haejun.

00:21:26.360 --> 00:21:28.220
You did it on purpose, didn't you?

00:21:29.380 --> 00:21:31.580
Why do you always stop kissing halfway?

00:21:32.450 --> 00:21:34.050
Because you like going slow.

00:21:35.590 --> 00:21:37.190
I'm just matching your pace.

00:21:39.380 --> 00:21:41.580
You haven't given me a new year gift yet.

00:21:42.130 --> 00:21:43.530
I won't just let it slide.

00:21:45.370 --> 00:21:46.110
But...

00:21:46.970 --> 00:21:49.100
don't you think you're going too slow?

00:21:50.860 --> 00:21:51.530
Besides,

00:21:52.110 --> 00:21:55.110
you've only been kissing me
in secluded spots lately.

00:21:55.150 --> 00:21:57.610
Is Christmas season
getting you in the mood?

00:22:01.250 --> 00:22:02.710
Let's talk on the rooftop.

00:22:03.820 --> 00:22:04.950
Don't be impatient.

00:23:38.160 --> 00:23:39.580
You're so greedy.

00:23:41.620 --> 00:23:43.130
I'm so rich,

00:23:44.050 --> 00:23:45.710
yet you're calling me greedy?

00:23:47.550 --> 00:23:48.890
I'll show you

00:23:49.930 --> 00:23:50.990
what true greed is.

00:24:58.330 --> 00:24:59.060
What is this?

00:25:12.030 --> 00:25:14.830
Haejun, do you want to
bake cookies again tonight?

00:25:15.950 --> 00:25:16.470
No.

00:25:18.140 --> 00:25:19.780
I'm a bit tired.

00:25:39.860 --> 00:25:40.980
[Who are you?]

00:26:01.980 --> 00:26:14.920
[Tide of Love 2]

00:27:33.880 --> 00:27:42.520
[Tide of Love 2]